1
00:00:10,520 --> 00:00:11,680
Thank you.

2
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:04,599
It's done.

3
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:15,240
We leave at dawn as soon as there's a boat.

4
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:16,320
What about her?

5
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:23,000
Forget it. Families should be left out of this.

6
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,660
Just keep an eye on her for now.

7
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:37,360
We staked out downstairs at Tian Yongan's house all night.

8
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:38,759
He still hasn't shown up.

9
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:43,060
We're still missing Tian Yongan and Hong Jinyi.

10
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:47,640
You've been watching all night.

11
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,370
Get some sleep. I'll take over.

12
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:52,120
Wait a minute.

13
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:57,039
Zhang Ran sent a message.

14
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:58,700
Tian Yongan is on Zhijin Road.

15
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:00,840
Let's go.

16
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,259
As for this person,

17
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,600
I do know her.

18
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,900
She approached me.

19
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,600
But I went to her place

20
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,480
purely for work purposes.

21
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,880
When she saw I wasn't taking the bait,

22
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,840
she went to an old client of mine.

23
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,440
What old client of yours?

24
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:23,040
He's in real estate finance.

25
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:25,079
His name is Hong Jinyi.

26
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,040
Hong Jinyi.

27
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:26,760
Right.

28
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,360
He's drinking with Mr. Tian.

29
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,370
Mr. Tian is an old client of his.

30
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:33,440
Weren't you drinking with him last night?

31
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:35,500
I haven't seen Hong Jinyi for a while.

32
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:36,720
Oh no.

33
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,520
Thank you for your cooperation.

34
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,450
You're welcome.

35
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,440
I thought you were dead.

36
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:17,040
Don't kill me.

37
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,440
My boss didn't call,

38
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:19,960
so I won't kill you.

39
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,079
Lao Er, let's go.

40
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:50,960
Open the door.

41
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:56,000
Hong Jinyi.

42
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,880
Is Hong Jinyi at home?

43
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,400
I have a registered letter for you.

44
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,730
Come out and sign for it.

45
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:16,890
Second Brother!

46
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,459
Brother, you go first!

47
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,490
Second Brother!

48
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,560
Aiyuan, hurry!

49
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,160
I'm here.

50
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,040
Jump quickly!

51
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,120
Hurry up!

52
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,420
I'll catch you.

53
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:48,290
You stay here and watch him.

54
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,370
Hua Weihong, you are under arrest!

55
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,400
Are you okay?

56
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,240
Let's go!

57
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,040
Help me.

58
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,500
The police are coming.

59
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,640
Cut the crap.

60
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,600
Do I look like a cop to you?

61
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,400
Brother.

62
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,800
Think about it.

63
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:07,080
They haven't called you for so long.

64
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:10,280
Either they abandoned you and ran away.

65
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:13,520
Or they've been caught.

66
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:17,240
If you don't believe me, give them a call.

67
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:24,140
The number you dialed is powered off.

68
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:29,800
Brothers are the least trustworthy in this world.

69
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:35,200
They must have called the police to catch you.

70
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,330
You go get the money.

71
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:39,440
Brother, let her go.

72
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:42,200
Someone thinks she's really good at selling out.

73
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:42,800
Third Brother!

74
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,720
You always mess things up when there's a woman.

75
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,380
Second Brother, come with me.

76
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,760
Nuannuan.

77
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:05,840
Nuannuan.

78
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,720
Nuannuan, where are you, Nuannuan?

79
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:18,680
Nuannuan.

80
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:23,240
Nuannuan.

81
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,930
Nuannuan, are you okay?

82
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:28,260
Nuannuan, say something.

83
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,640
Don't scare Mommy.

84
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,680
Nuannuan.

85
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:40,890
Have you seen these two people?

86
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,000
Welcome.

87
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,240
Miss.

88
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:56,000
I want a room. Okay.

89
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,800
Miss, where's the elevator?

90
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:09,680
On your right.

91
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,160
M-Manager.

92
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,160
What's wrong?

93
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,600
Tell the truth.

94
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:43,059
Where are Hua Weihong and Cao Aiyuan?

95
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,800
I'd like to know where he is too.

96
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,520
If you can find him,

97
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,700
say hello to my brother for me.

98
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:53,080
Didn't realize you were a tough nut.

99
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:57,080
It's no fun to crack a tough nut, right?

100
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,400
Besides, Zhang Ran has already sent people

101
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:01,400
to block all routes out of Chudong.

102
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,300
Keep stalling.

103
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:05,160
I have plenty of time to wait you out.

104
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,400
We received a tip.

105
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:10,600
Hua Weihong and Cao Aiyuan were seen at the Shuixie Hotel.

106
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:16,000
I'll take him to your older brother for you.

107
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,320
Since you brothers are so close,

108
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,200
I have to bring him back.

109
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:20,330
You two can take your time catching up.

110
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:29,200
Who called the police?

111
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,080
I did.

112
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:30,800
Did you see them?

113
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:31,680
I did.

114
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:32,360
Are you sure it was them?

115
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:32,920
I'm sure.

116
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,880
What other exits are there besides the main entrance?

117
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:37,200
There's a back door and a side door.

118
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,520
Boys, keep a close watch on the back and side doors.

119
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:39,480
Okay.

120
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,640
What's their room number?

121
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,200
Room 611.

122
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,120
How long have they been up there?

123
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,200
About half an hour.

124
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:53,580
Captain Ma,

125
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:54,760
no one is here.

126
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,200
They didn't stay here at all.

127
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,600
It's a diversion.

128
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:07,880
They have already left Chudong.
